According to the petitioner, the western boundary of 
the St. Helena viticultural area is not strictly delineated 
by historical custom. The petitioner states that this 
western boundary should be dictated by the eastern boundary 
of the adjacent Spring Mountain District viticultural area 
which utilizes the 400-foot contour line. The petitioner 
states that although some people might draw the western 
boundary of the St. Helena viticultural area at the 500 or 
